go  and  make the next pick-up from Northampton Bus  Station,  the 
elusive James Mathews!! 

Now if I had got out of the car at that point,  just to look in on 
how  the party was running,  I might have found out about  James's 
cock up,  and the next hour might have gone differently, as it was 
though..

